Subject: [PATCH] cmake: Link sdl.hdll with OpenGL
Upstream: submitted
References: gh#HaxeFoundation/hashlink#516

On openSUSE the packages are build with -Wl,--no-undefined and it would fail because of missing symbols
---
 libs/sdl/CMakeLists.txt | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/libs/sdl/CMakeLists.txt b/libs/sdl/CMakeLists.txt
index 7c90646..facd788 100644
--- a/libs/sdl/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/libs/sdl/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -25,8 +25,8 @@ if(WIN32)
     )
 endif()
 
-if(APPLE)
-    find_package(OPENGL REQUIRED)
+if(APPLE OR UNIX)
+    find_package(OpenGL REQUIRED)
     target_include_directories(sdl.hdll
         PRIVATE
         ${OPENGL_INCLUDE_DIR}
